Iman Essa Jasim (nke a na-akpọkwa Jassim ma ọ bụ Jassem, amụrụ na 9 Julaị 1997) bụ onye na-agba ọsọ na Bahraini. O sonyere ṅa asọmpi 100 mita ụmụ nwanyị na 2016 Summer Olympics A mụrụ ya na Endurance Essien Udoh na Naijirịa na 9 Julaị 1997.

Na 2016 Asian Indoor Athletics Championships ndị otu ya nke gụnyere Salwa Eid Naser, Kemi Adekoya, na Aminat Yusuf Jamal setịpụrụ ndekọ ọhụrụ nke Asia na Championships nke 3:35.07 na ihe omume 4 × 400 m nke ụmụ nwanyị.
